description: Welcome to Fort Point Place, an iconic loft building in Boston's historic and rapidly developing Fort Point. #517 is a chic loft in one of Boston’s most sought-after neighborhoods. Just steps from the Seaport, this spacious 1,025 sq/ft home blends historic charm with modern luxury, featuring soaring ceilings, oversized windows, exposed beams, and wide-plank maple floors. The custom kitchen boasts soapstone countertops, Bosch and KitchenAid appliances, a subway tile backsplash, and bespoke pendant lighting. The serene bedroom accommodates a king-sized bed with double closets, while the bath offers a marble-top vanity and a full-capacity Maytag washer and dryer. With its seamless fusion of industrial character and contemporary elegance, this Fort Point loft offers an unparalleled urban living experience. *Photos virtually staged.
